			<useAdviceForDataSet xml:lang="en">When using this dataset for Life Cycle Assessment, ensure that the boundaries of the LCA study include the thermal desorption process and the transport of soil if applicable. Consider the environmental impacts of both the remediation process and the subsequent handling of the treated soil. It is important to verify that the quality assessment of the remediated soil aligns with the local regulations and intended use of the backfilled area. The dataset should not be used for soil that is to be disposed of without this treatment process or for other forms of soil remediation.</useAdviceForDataSet>
			<useAdviceForDataSet xml:lang="zh">在使用此数据集进行生命周期评估时，请确保LCA研究的边界包括热脱附过程和土壤运输（如果适用）。考虑到修复过程及后续处理经过处理土壤的环境影响。重要的是要验证经修复土壤的质量评估是否符合当地法规和回填区域的预期用途。该数据集不应用于未经此处理过程就处置的土壤，或其他形式的土壤修复。</useAdviceForDataSet>
